// awesome console plagin - for terminal clickable path
`File | Settings | Editor | Color Scheme | General > Editor > Gutter background`

Ctrl+D  //  Дублировать строку под курсором.
Ctrl+Y  //  Удалить строку под курсором.
alt + f12 // open terminal
Ctrl+P brings up a list of valid parameters (If the cursor is between the parentheses of a method call).
Ctrl+Shift+F // find
Ctrl+Shift+R // replace
Ctrl+f then alt+j // select occurrence
alt + 1 // open file sidebar

terminal caret // :( https://www.jetbrains.com/help/idea/terminal-emulator.html
File > Settings... > Editor > Code Style > Hard wrap at  // line length

alt+f12 then esc // switch between terminal and editor

Press Ctrl twice, and then without releasing it, press up or down arrow keys.  // multi caret
shift + alt + click

Ctrl + up/down   // move line up/down

alt + shift + right/left arrow // go back/forward

Ctrl+N - find class
Ctrl+f12 - method list
Ctrl+b - go to

tips
alt+shift+7 // all occurrence (usages)


